text:
Hey all, I have a question regarding how HubSpot and HUBL (require_js) is loading and inserting javascript files into our website twice. i.e. Inserting our google maps scripts twice on the page.  Since the issue relates to JS, i figure this is a good place?

Essentially, I'm adding a require_js('url') in my module, but the end result in the page source, it's added twice causing google maps errors... Has anyone come across this?

do you have multiple modules with this requirement?

are you doing this in code or in the ui?

can you share the page url and your code for us to look at?

using require js should only load on page once per page if this is set up correctly
